ARCTIC.
KARA SEA.
RUSSIA.
1. SEISMIC SURVEY IN PROGRESS UNTIL 15 NOV
   BY M/V VYACHESLAV TIKHONOV TOWING EIGHT
   6000 METER LONG CABLES IN AREA BOUND BY
   73-11.0N 068-17.0E, 73-08.2N 068-51.7E,
   72-47.3N 068-41.6E, 72-47.6N 068-06.5E.

3. CANCEL THIS MSG 16 NOV 14.
